Description: These are the actual Matte with brown (looks light brown but is dark when you where them). Yes, the actual ones which are hard to find. I see a lot of people selling the glossy version of this as if it were this one but I shake my head when I see those ones pop up. These go for upwards of $130 but these were very gently used so I cannot say that they are new but they are in very good condition. Take a look at the pictures for a full description on what you are getting and definitely pick the right ones. Yes these are the right ones which I had my brother send me several pair of while he worked at Oakley in Irvine, CA. Don't worry, I'm keeping a few of them. I just don't need 4 pairs. Good luck and hope you have a wonderful day! I do not have the original box for this one but it does come with the sleeve.
